arts.ttl: Chelsea draw up Andrey Santos transfer plan for 2025
arts.sum: Chelsea have earmarked Andrey Santos for a place in Enzo Maresca's squad next season, according to a report. Santos spent a brief period on loan in Alsace after the January window and impressed in limited minutes following his lengthy international duty in Brazil for Olympic preparations.
